  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize move_to_marker_commit immediately upon marker_seen.",
    "Commit to forward or rotation actions to avoid dithering.",
    "After obstacle detection, always pass through scan_full before resuming forward.",
    "Alternate between forward_commit and scan_full to ensure regular scanning.",
    "Use rotate_commit states to persist in a chosen turn direction until path is clear.",
    "Upon marker_close, enter marker_close_stop and stop movement.",
    "Never allow move_forward after obstacle_front without recovery.",
    "Do not allow oscillatory rotation choices in any state.",
    "If marker is lost, resume exploration via scan_full and forward_commit alternation."
